# Old stable

This branch of **awesome** is deprecated. However bug fixes are still welcome.

Latest old stable version of **awesome** is version 2.3.6 (*Tomorrow Morning*) released on 18th April 2009.

* [v2.3.6 changelog](/changelogs/v2.3.6) ([short](/changelogs/short/v2.3.6))
